snippet.title: Aspire: Ina's Tale Announcement | PC, Switch, Xbox One
snippet.description:
https://aspireinastale.com/

Set out on a fantastical adventure as Ina and take a journey of self-discovery against the backdrop of dazzling, mystical landscapes of The Tower. Experience her fear turn to conviction as she unravels her purpose in this world and embarks on a one-way path to freedom

Wishlist on Steam today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1720090/Aspire_Inas_Tale/
To keep up with Untold Tales and Aspire: Ina's Tale, use the following links: 

Website: https://untoldtales.games/ 
Facebook: https://facebook.com/untoldtalesgames 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/untoldtalesHQ
